{"tid":124394,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實七警直接認罪係咪仲好","createTime":"2017-02-17T14:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T12:47:03.000Z","uid":4528,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a850bf20c8485a01f8769d60c7b4169e7b70329b","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"高層出面咁撐佢地<br />\n「你地無做錯到！」<br />\n又話大律師 又話幫佢地籌錢<br />\n依家連認罪扣減刑期都無<br />\n<br />\n我覺得七警仆街就抵死，因為佢地有濫用職權打人，知法犯法，同唔識法律的示威者打人唔同。<br />\n但係後面推波助瀾果班藍絲，捐錢出黎話幫七警果班，同警隊高層出面撐果班，三班人害到佢地咁！<br />\n<br />\n唔通七警七個都覺得自己真係無做錯到？<br />\n定係依個「自己人撐自己人」依種盲撐心態，害到佢地唔識得認錯？"},{"pid":"7ddbf5a3ae2c560395eae8da1c1112c29205d841","tid":124394,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:19:02.000Z","msg":"因為政治智慧不足<br />\n誤以為自己會有政治庇護<br />\n點知比人拎黎做祭品"},{"pid":"2584fb98099639fbb5c39ff7a0df73666c88fdec","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢地比人煽動左<br />\n警員如果支持反佔中，要堅實地遵守法律<br />\n一個華麗轉身就打人<br />\n又話大壓力又成，求哂情咁<br />\n但係又屌佔中班人，話點樣犯法都錯<br />\n<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"001422bc98e1a7ca058b03ed4e64f0e0c8ca44eb","tid":124394,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得佢地比人煽動左<br />\n警員如果支持反佔中，要堅實地遵守法律<br />\n一個華麗轉身就打人<br />\n又話大壓力又成，求哂情咁<br />\n但係又屌佔中班人，話點樣犯法都錯<br />\n<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠</blockquote><br />\n正宗賊喊捉賊"},{"pid":"939b02759bf1f6c22cadad1e0f408cc50bf7499d","tid":124394,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得佢地比人<span style=\"color: red;\">煽動左</span><br />\n警員如果支持反佔中，要堅實地遵守法律<br />\n一個華麗轉身就打人<br />\n又話大壓力又成，求哂情咁<br />\n但係又屌佔中班人，話點樣犯法都錯<br />\n<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定曾經有高層話冇事，一哥會照住你地，你地唔好認罪<br />\n<br />\n最後奶野，成為活祭品"},{"pid":"b0bc7da6293429570bbb88cc97619766d04434c1","tid":124394,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"根本冇做錯到<br />\n認咩罪姐"},{"pid":"10a482a7b9bd7b28cb8de4ea59b3b46cc435f1b4","tid":124394,"uid":53011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"只可以話抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad00c8b12f5c789e77828a48189aa710033051a","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會係關乎整個警隊的面子<br />\n所以唔可以認錯？<br />\n定係佢地真心覺得自己無錯？<br />\n<br />\n真心認罪，可以扣減1/3呀 成幾個月喎"},{"pid":"623e1033f894958809d4f7825fd6bef71a6b5863","tid":124394,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本冇做錯到<br />\n認咩罪姐</blockquote><br />\n同意，佢地冇錯<br />\n係法律既錯、社會既錯"},{"pid":"38d9fca7115aab951733dc147177116109a6b96f","tid":124394,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:29:24.000Z","msg":"唔好認<br />\n一定要上訴<br />\n洗多幾球野<br />\n排期排到刑期滿都未有得審<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828ff0f70f79a604e302ef8df7ca2b93feaf5c46","tid":124394,"uid":62314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"認左罪，準備多啲求情信扮下死狗應該隨時坐三個月左右，啲網上五毛真係害撚死佢地，又話段片唔完整又話認唔到樣告唔入，依家入撚左全世界講埋啲野都係默認七警打左人但唔應該判咁重，再上訴都唔會打得甩"},{"pid":"c353f4ce695088b5ba3cfff168ea3547853d7946","tid":124394,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人"},{"pid":"769696863ee263a678dfa0d34f938c13e21b076d","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"七個警察 真係一個認罪都無喎！<br />\n真係唔認錯<br />\n只可以罰重少少<br />\n等佢地係入面反省"},{"pid":"08c364aba9573b05094a3efa86d848bb20823b59","tid":124394,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 爆蛋勇士 )"},{"pid":"5a4bf3d2139f7af08789c71a892c18d1522175c8","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n依家暫時判咗有罪，暫時當證據確鑿先。<br />\n問題係佢地有無咁做先？<br />\n如果有，點解唔直接認罪？<br />\n知錯能改呀！ 唔知錯點改！<br />\n仲要七個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063eaa7b59636ad5c1a85a6900a89dbedb8a15ce","tid":124394,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"你味block鳩我law"},{"pid":"ef61d4e51c4b2b6672325a7f5e919b9ed0849a8e","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你味block鳩我law</blockquote><br />\n你試下回應下我的睇法"},{"pid":"1160566067ebce98061cce9e3b70b17f86a7efda","tid":124394,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n做得警察 點都有承擔啦下話<br />\n咁大個男人 做錯咪應 打就企定<br />\n仲要期望告唔入 好撚肉酸成件事<br />\n<br />\n七個警察都覺得係咁，我只可以講好失望。<br />\n如果係班高層教佢地唔好認，咁樣好仆街囉。"},{"pid":"a4faae49fd8ed2113dc57d18b2c73f1402a32127","tid":124394,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n依家暫時判咗有罪，暫時當證據確鑿先。<br />\n問題係佢地有無咁做先？<br />\n如果有，點解唔直接認罪？<br />\n知錯能改呀！ 唔知錯點改！<br />\n仲要七個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係當，係已經&quot;證據確鑿&quot;咗<br />\n上訴只係爭拗法律觀點，唔會推翻下級法院嘅evidence<br />\n即係其實已經confirm 咗係佢哋7個，再上訴只係會爭拗係咪真係襲擊罪，會唔會判得太重之類<br />\n(有錯請指證)"},{"pid":"ce604eb9e44728248d095bf64e268880a328f0b0","tid":124394,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n做得警察 點都有承擔啦下話<br />\n咁大個男人 做錯咪應 打就企定<br />\n仲要期望告唔入 好撚肉酸成件事<br />\n<br />\n七個警察都覺得係咁，我只可以講好失望。<br />\n如果係班高層教佢地唔好認，咁樣好仆街囉。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個係咁諗警察冇壞人啦&hellip;有承擔&hellip;"},{"pid":"09e8823947e051f89e5aebed0faf0c9f0499715b","tid":124394,"uid":10163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 爆蛋勇士 )<br />\n連登真係多弱智"},{"pid":"498c7240f566e072b0cf57ad5648afd8ee0014ba","tid":124394,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n點唔100%法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c46d24208e90e4f81d2c12b5b6cc888a4bc156e","tid":124394,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n點唔100%法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法庭判咗係就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e76d5cb4ccbe0d389ad80c3d4a164fc79052808","tid":124394,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"做咩撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555a4f44116fd1bb2e700465f6a9011476a1aaf4","tid":124394,"uid":65286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>段片有好多懷疑的地方<br />\n都不能夠100%證明當時是他們7個人</blockquote><br />\n點唔100%法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法庭判咗係就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實7警有打人，所以判罪都好合理，但另一方面警方高層唔攬佢地又真係唔得"}]}